659
00:51:39,725 --> 00:51:41,651
Thank you so much.

660
00:51:55,156 --> 00:51:58,459
- Here you go. Thank you.
- Thank you.

661
00:51:59,536 --> 00:52:01,879
- Hello.
- Thank you.

662
00:52:10,088 --> 00:52:12,549
Thank you, Mr. Sasae.

663
00:52:12,549 --> 00:52:15,802
I was incredibly moved by your novel.

664
00:52:15,802 --> 00:52:17,595
Thank you.

665
00:52:17,595 --> 00:52:20,115
Your Japanese is very good.

666
00:52:20,115 --> 00:52:21,683
Really?

667
00:52:21,683 --> 00:52:23,533
I'm studying Japanese

668
00:52:23,533 --> 00:52:26,604
thanks to your novel.

669
00:52:26,604 --> 00:52:29,532
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

670
00:52:34,654 --> 00:52:37,164
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

671
00:52:42,412 --> 00:52:43,985
Sir.

672
00:52:45,791 --> 00:52:47,398
Choi Hong.

673
00:52:48,796 --> 00:52:50,096
You know her...

674
00:52:50,096 --> 00:52:51,546
Right?

